WEBVTT

00:00.233 --> 00:01.913
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:01.933 --> 00:04.532
I'm coming get you in the Mustang
and cool stuff. I'll be fun.

00:04.546 --> 00:05.947
- Ok.
- I'll see you in two weeks.

00:05.980 --> 00:07.980
- Are you getting.
- No.

00:07.981 --> 00:11.892
What is that even mean?

00:11.919 --> 00:14.788
I hate you! I hate...

00:14.790 --> 00:16.122
Help!

00:16.123 --> 00:18.191
- Hey, what's going on?
- What happened?

00:18.193 --> 00:19.559
<i>Something's wrong with the twins.</i>

00:19.561 --> 00:21.394
What?

00:22.497 --> 00:23.930
Things are falling through the cracks

00:23.932 --> 00:26.132
every day that Mac is in jail.

00:26.134 --> 00:28.068
- You know they are.
- I'll talk to Connie again.

00:28.070 --> 00:30.203
And here's what
you're going to tell her.

00:30.205 --> 00:31.571
I'm going to preach.

00:31.573 --> 00:34.441
Not you, not Grace. Me.

00:34.443 --> 00:36.343
- Mae...
- Just for a while.

00:36.345 --> 00:37.878
When did this happen?

00:37.880 --> 00:41.181
I got the notice of seizure from
the city a couple months ago.

00:41.183 --> 00:44.684
<i>Whoever Mac has in his pocket
at city hall ain't budging.</i>

00:44.686 --> 00:46.143
Is there any way out?

00:46.168 --> 00:47.787
Bishop: <i>There's always
a way out, you know that.</i>

00:47.789 --> 00:50.290
You just have to confess.

